{
  "id": "61e91b382199d5001d170250",
  "title": "(2.2.3.1) Exploration-exploitation tradeoff",
  "created": 1548667950,
  "updated": 1554540165,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f947",
      "text": "(2.2.3.1) Exploration-exploitation tradeoff",
      "created": 1548667950,
      "updated": 1553587206,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f948",
      "text": "This problem is called '[exploration-exploitation tradeoff]' in the field of [reinforcement learning]. You can not find better options if you choose only the option that looks the best from your experiences. It is a lack of [exploration]. (*1)",
      "created": 1548667950,
      "updated": 1554540165,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f949",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548667950,
      "updated": 1548667950,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f94a",
      "text": "On the other hand, if you are looking for better options and only choosing inexperienced options, your experiences are not used. It is a lack of [exploitation].",
      "created": 1548667950,
      "updated": 1554540158,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f94b",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548667950,
      "updated": 1548667950,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f94c",
      "text": "Since exploration and exploitation are in a trade-off relationship, it is necessary to execute both in a well-balanced manner, not on one side. So how can we make the well-balanced choices?",
      "created": 1548667950,
      "updated": 1548667950,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f94d",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548667950,
      "updated": 1548667950,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f94e",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1553587222,
      "updated": 1553587223,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f94f",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548825045,
      "updated": 1548825045,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
