    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f952",
      "text": "\tThe discussion went detail in the field of [reinforcement learning]. ",
      "created": 1548825129,
      "updated": 1548825174,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f953",
      "text": "\t\thttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multi-armed_bandit",
      "created": 1548825174,
      "updated": 1548825174,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f954",
      "text": "\tHowever, its origin is unclear. The cencept is used in wide domain.",
